    {
      "font": "hardcore_discs:comic_sans_ut",
      "text": "gotta say!"
    },
    "Hear the birds singing while these flowers bloom",
    "See those church bells ringing",
    "Now they're sounding out your doom!",
    "Seems this trio's a bit much for you with-",
    "",
