    {"setFont": "hardcore_discs:comic_sans_ut"},
    "wait!",
    "",
    "one last chance,",
    "it's in your hands",
    "i'm begging you to bring it back",
    [
      {"text": "(Bring it back...)", "font": "hardcore_discs:dotumche"}
    ],
    "a world where monsters hoped and dreamed,",
    [
      {"text": "(Or don't!)", "font": "hardcore_discs:dotumche"}
    ],
    "a world that used to have meaning...",
    [
      {"text": "(BUT YOU WON'T.)", "font": "hardcore_discs:papyrus_ut"}
    ],
    "you went and tore it all to shreds",
    [
      {"text": "(YOU'VE NOT ONE REGRET...", "font": "hardcore_discs:papyrus_ut"}
