    "left every last one of 'em dead",
    "...you know what?",
    "i tried.",
    "guess this is...",
    "goodbye.",
    "",
    {"setFont": "hardcore_discs:dtm_sans"},
    "Here at the end",
    "Even without friends",
    [
      {"text": "Determined", "color": "#FF0001"}
    ],
    "Is there still a chance to stop your advance?",
    "Everyone you dusted",
    "After how we trusted you",
    "Us three already know that we might lose",
    "Looking around, everything is gray",
    "Gotta' say-",
    "Can't help but thinking this'll be our tomb",
    "Church bells kept on ringing",
    "Now they're sounding out our doom",
    "Seems this trio wasn't enough for you...",
    "",
    "Knife in hand",
    "Determined as ever you stand...",
    "What in hell's name",
    "Might it take for your will to break..?",
    {"setFont": "hardcore_discs:papyrus_ut"},
    "WITH HATRED LIKE YOURS, HOW CAN WE WIN?",
